msgstr ""
"# aptitude -y -s -f --with-recommends dist-upgrade\n"
"[ ... ]\n"
"XXX 个已升级，XXX 个刚装上，XXX 个待删除以及 XXX 个未升级。\n"
"需要获取 xx.xMB/yyyMB。解开后，将占用 AAAMB。\n"
